videos.headline: Syracuse strikes first with QB sneak
videos.description: QB Eric Dungey puts his head down and fights his way across the goal line to give the Orange a 7-0 lead.

videos.headline: Dungey registers 2nd rushing TD vs. UConn
videos.description: Syracuse QB Eric Dungey drags defenders into the end zone for a 9-yard touchdown run, making it 14-0 Orange.

videos.headline: UConn QB takes off for 75-yard TD
videos.description: QB David Pindell makes a man miss and outruns the Syracuse defense for a 75-yard Huskies touchdown.

videos.headline: UConn hangs around with 2-yard TD pass
videos.description: QB David Pindell rolls to his right and connects with RB Zavier Scott to keep the Huskies within striking distance of the Orange.

videos.headline: Dungey scores 3rd rushing TD of half
videos.description: QB Eric Dungey gets behind his blockers and finds paydirt to pad Syracuse's lead against UConn.

videos.headline: Riley goes 49 yards for 2nd TD reception of game
videos.description: Eric Dungey connects with WR Sean Riley over the middle, who shows off his speed on his way to the end zone.
